lines.text: All mimsy were ye borogoves; and ye mome raths outgrabe.
Ah-ha! Hahahaha! So, dear brother, you bring Dirk here? Caligenous, clanking piece of junk! Boil in the mud, you meddling, old fool! Dirk will be helpless, once you've been sunk! Hahahahahahaha!
You want Daphne? Hahahahahaha! Go get her!
Daphne's mine! Farewell, you fool! Hahahahahahahaha!
